---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro'
---

<Base
  title="xNet — Decentralized Data Infrastructure"
  description="Local-first, P2P-synced, user-owned data. From personal notes to planetary-scale indexes."
>
  <!-- Nav -->
  <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-border bg-[#0a0a0f]/80 backdrop-blur-md">
    <nav class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
      <a href={import.meta.env.BASE_URL} class="font-mono text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white hover:text-indigo-400 transition-colors">
        xNet
      </a>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm">
        <a href="#features" class="hidden sm:inline text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Features</a>
        <a href="#architecture" class="hidden sm:inline text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Architecture</a>
        <a href="#get-started" class="hidden sm:inline text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Get Started</a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/anomalyco/xNet"
          class="rounded-md border border-border px-3 py-1.5 text-gray-200 hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-surface transition-all"
        >
          GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl grid-cols-1 items-center gap-12 px-6 py-24 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 lg:py-32">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-[3.5rem]">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-indigo-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Your data.<br/>Your devices.<br/>Your rules.
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-md text-lg text-gray-400">
          xNet is decentralized data infrastructure. Local-first, P2P-synced,
          user-owned. From personal notes to planetary-scale indexes.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4">
          <a
            href="https://github.com/anomalyco/xNet"
            class="rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 px-5 py-2.5 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-indigo-500 transition-colors"
          >
            View on GitHub
          </a>
          <a
            href="#features"
            class="rounded-lg border border-border px-5 py-2.5 font-semibold text-gray-200 hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-surface transition-all"
          >
            Learn More
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400"><code><span class="text-indigo-400">import</span> {'{'} defineSchema, text, select {'}'} <span class="text-indigo-400">from</span> <span class="text-emerald-400">'@xnet/data'</span>

<span class="text-indigo-400">const</span> TaskSchema = <span class="text-yellow-300">defineSchema</span>({'{'}
  name: <span class="text-emerald-400">'Task'</span>,
  namespace: <span class="text-emerald-400">'xnet://myapp/'</span>,
  properties: {'{'}
    title: <span class="text-yellow-300">text</span>({'{'} required: <span class="text-orange-400">true</span> {'}'}),
    status: <span class="text-yellow-300">select</span>({'{'}
      options: [<span class="text-emerald-400">'todo'</span>, <span class="text-emerald-400">'in-progress'</span>, <span class="text-emerald-400">'done'</span>]
    {'}'})
  {'}'}
{'}'})</code></pre>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section id="features" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Built Different</h2>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-6 transition-colors hover:border-indigo-500/40">
          <div class="text-2xl">&#9741;</div>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold">Local-First</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
            Works offline. Syncs when connected. Your data lives on your devices, not someone else's server.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-6 transition-colors hover:border-indigo-500/40">
          <div class="text-2xl">&#8644;</div>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold">P2P Synced</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
            Devices sync directly via WebRTC. No central server required. CRDTs handle conflicts automatically.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-6 transition-colors hover:border-indigo-500/40">
          <div class="text-2xl">&#128273;</div>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold">Cryptographic Identity</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
            DID:key identities with Ed25519 signing. UCAN tokens for fine-grained, delegatable permissions.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-6 transition-colors hover:border-indigo-500/40">
          <div class="text-2xl">&#128209;</div>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold">Schema-First</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
            Define your data model with TypeScript-inferred schemas. Everything is a Node, typed by its Schema.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-6 transition-colors hover:border-indigo-500/40">
          <div class="text-2xl">&#9997;</div>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold">Real-Time Collaboration</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
            Rich text editing with Yjs CRDTs. Character-level merge for documents, field-level LWW for structured data.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-6 transition-colors hover:border-indigo-500/40">
          <div class="text-2xl">&#128268;</div>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold">Plugin Extensible</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
            Extend with custom schemas, views, and integrations. ERP, knowledge bases, or anything you build.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Architecture -->
    <section id="architecture" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Architecture</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-400">Same primitives from personal notes to global indexes</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 rounded-lg border border-border border-l-[3px] border-l-blue-400 px-5 py-4">
          <span class="min-w-[100px] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-blue-400">Macro</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-400">Decentralized Search &middot; Federated Social &middot; Public Datasets</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 rounded-lg border border-border border-l-[3px] border-l-amber-400 px-5 py-4">
          <span class="min-w-[100px] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-amber-400">Organization</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-400">Team Workspaces &middot; Audit Trails &middot; Access Control</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 rounded-lg border border-border border-l-[3px] border-l-emerald-400 px-5 py-4">
          <span class="min-w-[100px] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400">Personal</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-400">Notes &middot; Tasks &middot; Databases &middot; Private by Default</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
          <code class="rounded-md border border-border bg-surface px-3 py-1.5 text-xs text-gray-300">Node</code>
          <code class="rounded-md border border-border bg-surface px-3 py-1.5 text-xs text-gray-300">Schema</code>
          <code class="rounded-md border border-border bg-surface px-3 py-1.5 text-xs text-gray-300">CRDT Sync</code>
          <code class="rounded-md border border-border bg-surface px-3 py-1.5 text-xs text-gray-300">DID + UCAN</code>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Tech Stack -->
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Under the Hood</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-indigo-400">Sync</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Yjs CRDT for rich text. Event-sourced changes with Lamport clocks for structured data.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-indigo-400">Crypto</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">BLAKE3 hashing. Ed25519 signing. XChaCha20-Poly1305 encryption. All in the browser.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-indigo-400">Network</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">libp2p transport. WebRTC direct connections. Optional hub relay for always-on sync.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-indigo-400">Storage</h4>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">IndexedDB on web. SQLite on desktop/mobile. Content-addressed with CIDs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Platforms -->
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Cross-Platform</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface px-5 py-4">
          <strong>Desktop</strong>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Electron (macOS, Linux, Windows)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface px-5 py-4">
          <strong>Mobile</strong>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Expo (iOS, Android)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface px-5 py-4">
          <strong>Web</strong>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">PWA (any browser)</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Get Started -->
    <section id="get-started" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Get Started</h2>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-md text-left">
        <pre class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-5 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400"><code>git clone https://github.com/anomalyco/xNet.git
cd xNet
pnpm install
pnpm dev</code></pre>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
        Requires Node.js 22+ and pnpm. See the
        <a href="https://github.com/anomalyco/xNet" class="text-indigo-400 hover:underline">README</a> for full setup.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="border-t border-border">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-6 text-sm text-gray-500">
      <span class="font-mono font-bold text-gray-300">xNet</span>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <a href="https://github.com/anomalyco/xNet" class="hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">GitHub</a>
        <span>&middot;</span>
        <a href="https://github.com/anomalyco/xNet/blob/main/LICENSE" class="hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">MIT License</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Base>
